name: Dunsparce
author: Mitsuhiro Arita
flavor_text: It digs into the ground with its tail and makes a mazelike nest. It can fly just a little.

attacks.name: Strike and Run
attacks.effect: Search your deck for up to 3 Basic Pokémon and put them onto your Bench. Then, shuffle your deck. If you put any Pokémon onto your Bench in this way, you may switch this Pokémon with 1 of your Benched Pokémon.

attacks.name: Sudden Flash
attacks.effect: Flip a coin. If heads, your opponent’s Active Pokémon is now Paralyzed.
